    "rationale": "Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed the required gradation level. The single below-requirement factor (Test conditions, achieved 2 vs. required 3) is acknowledged as a credibility gap; however, the validation evidence as a whole—including quantitative output comparison satisfying E/uval < 1.96 and <10% QoI difference across N=11 constructs at two independent laboratories—provides sufficient confidence to support the intended COU decision at Medium model risk. The assessment team accepts the package with the noted limitation on test condition breadth.",
